buyNFT(uint256).details: Buy an NFT listed for sale

params._tokenId: The ID of the token being bought

getAllActiveListingsBySeller(address).details: Get all active listings by seller, i.e. listings that have not expired

getValueWithFeeApplied(address,uint256).details: Get the value of a payment with the fee applied

listNFT(uint256,uint256).details: List an NFT for sale and transferring token ownership to the marketplace contract

params._price: The price at which the token is listed for sale
params._tokenId: The ID of the token being listed for sale

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby disabling any functionality that is only available to the owner.

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

unlistNFT(uint256).details: Unlist an NFT listed for sale

params._tokenId: The ID of the token being unlisted

withdraw().notice: Withdraw the accumulated fee value and send to the owner

userdoc.notice: This contract is a marketplace for the Reservation NFTs
